title: West Palm Beach: New and Innovative Customized Dating Itinerary Service
text:
So…what do you wanna do tonight? West Palm Beach has the answer West Palm Beach: New and Innovative Customized Dating Itinerary Service Adv: 
Aug 08, 2015 Adv: 
New to Palm Beach, a wholly owned subsidiary of Baldrica Advertising and Marketing in West Palm Beach that promotes local businesses through their website and social media network is proud to announce a new customized dating itinerary service called Date Design Pros (R). 
This service, which is already available on the website, allows visitors to enter their date activity preferences from over 20 choices such as dining, water sports, beaches and sightseeing along with other demographic information so that the pros at New to Palm Beach can create a custom date itinerary. 
To officially launch this service, New to Palm Beach is holding the Best Date Ever contest party at the Majestic Princess 
The list of participating sponsors: 
South Florida Science Center – West Palm Beach Palm Beach Zoo – West Palm Beach Grassy Waters Preserve - Jupiter Cabo Flats – West Palm Beach Burger Bar – North Palm Beach Gondolas West – Ft. Lauderdale Sailfish Marina – West Palm Beach Real Deal Bicycles - Jupiter The Living Room – Boynton Beach The Waterway Cafe The Melting Pot – North Palm Beach Uptown Art – Delray, West Palm Beach & Jupiter N2 Winebar – Delray Avocado Grill – West Palm Beach The Brewhouse Gallery – Lake Park Royal Crown Luxury Travel – Transportation Sun Spray Tanning and Boutique – Spray Tan Cabo Flats Local Dines.com/South Florida The Kayak Kings 
The founders of New to Palm Beach are sure the event will help springboard their new Date Design Pros service that helps couples answer that dreaded question : "So…what do you wanna do tonight?"
